    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Staraway is a narrative-centric adventure about finding yourself in a weird little universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is a very short game! You will likely be able to beat it in under 2 hours.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Travel the stars!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your magical telescope to warp to distant star systems. Chart the sky with constellations you find and stars you visit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076330/extras/72fe7e396214d887183ebeb86a805bb6.poster.avif?t=1762580431\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076330/extras/72fe7e396214d887183ebeb86a805bb6.webm?t=1762580431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076330/extras/72fe7e396214d887183ebeb86a805bb6.mp4?t=1762580431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore tiny planets!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hop between bite-sized moons, asteroids, and planets. The world is always set in motion with the rotation of celestial bodies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076330/extras/0569e315758db2acec52666ab83aafd2.poster.avif?t=1762580431\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076330/extras/0569e315758db2acec52666ab83aafd2.webm?t=1762580431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076330/extras/0569e315758db2acec52666ab83aafd2.mp4?t=1762580431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Is everything okay?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Staraway is a short story about struggling with a strange dissonance, going through changes, and finding your way home. You won't make the journey alone, though.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3076330/extras/c67c82dbd6ac7b3106b0182bd3d24449.avif?t=1762580431\" width=616 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chill vibes!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Listen to a (mostly) calming electronic soundtrack that scores the story and intertwines with the world.</p>",
